{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/size-your-images","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-css","demoType":null,"title":"Podesi Velicinu Slika","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>CSS ima svojstvo <code>width</code> koje kontrolise sirinu elementa. Kao i kod fontova, koristicemo <code>px</code> (piksele) da odredimo sirinu slike.</p>\n<p>Na primer, kada bismo zeleli da napravimo CSS klasu <code>larger-image</code> koja daje HTML elementima sirinu od 500 piksela, koristili bismo:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&#x3C;style>\n  .larger-image {\n    width: 500px;\n  }\n&#x3C;/style>\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9acdf08812","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napravite klasu pod nazivom <code>smaller-image</code> i upotrebite je da promenite velicinu slike na sirinu od samo 100 piksela.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18282,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/size-your-images"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n<style>\n  .red-text {\n    color: red;\n  }\n\n  h2 {\n    font-family: Lobster, monospace;\n  }\n\n  p {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-family: monospace;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<h2 class=\"red-text\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\n<main>\n  <p class=\"red-text\">Click here to view more <a href=\"#\">cat photos</a>.</p>\n\n  <a href=\"#\"><img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\n\n  <div>\n    <p>Things cats love:</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li>catnip</li>\n      <li>laser pointers</li>\n      <li>lasagna</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\n    <ol>\n      <li>flea treatment</li>\n      <li>thunder</li>\n      <li>other cats</li>\n    </ol>\n  </div>\n\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\" checked> Indoor</label>\n    <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label><br>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\" checked> Loving</label>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\n    <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Energetic</label><br>\n    <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\n    <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n  </form>\n</main>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vas <code>img</code> element treba da ima klasu <code>smaller-image</code>.</p>","testString":"const relaxingCatImage = document.querySelector(\"img[src='https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg']\");\nconst catImageClass = relaxingCatImage.getAttribute('class').trim().split(/\\s+/g);\nassert.include(catImageClass, 'smaller-image');"},{"text":"<p>Vasa slika treba da ima sirinu od 100 piksela.</p>","testString":"const image = document.querySelector('img');\nconst width = image.getBoundingClientRect().width;\nassert.isBelow(width, 200); \nassert.match(__helpers.removeCssComments(code), /\\.smaller-image\\s*{\\s*width\\s*:\\s*100px\\s*(;\\s*}|})/i);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#basic-css","dashedName":"size-your-images","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-css","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/add-borders-around-your-elements","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/specify-how-fonts-should-degrade","id":"bad87fee1348bd9acdf08812","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>@media (max-width: 350px) {:root {--penguin-size: 200px; --penguin-skin: black;}}</style>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/basic-css/size-your-images"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}